author: Jason Brennan
title: Live Euro 2016 Qualifier - Ireland vs Poland
text: After the heroics of the Germany game, the boys in green travel to Stadion Narodowy in Warsaw to take on Poland. It's a daunting trip, with a lot on the line, but as we proved on Thursday night, we're obviously the best team in the world. So with no hint of bandwagoning, and zero biased, we can safely say we're going to stuff the Poles 5-0. #COYBIG
